Realtime,ORTC,is,a,real,time,cloud,hosted,messaging,solution,for,web,and,mobile,applications,Realtime,ORTC,delivers,messages,content,and,data,to,a,variety,of,platforms,and,devices,and,across,applications,The,Realtime,ORTC,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,integrate,the,functionality,of,Realtime,ORTC,with,other,applications,Some,example,API,methods,include,sending,messages,managing,account,and,user,information,and,accessing,content